{"tid":2174511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"質疑證人拍跌被告致撞沙展  官拒納兩差人證供 青年脫襲警罪","createTime":"2020-08-26T02:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T02:54:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"349df2da8bd90b8c378e61d63913e8f5751725a0","tid":2174511,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/EXUBUXT3ANABJF3NXQ4VHLHBZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FEXUBUXT3ANABJF3NXQ4VHLHBZI%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=412611a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FEXUBUXT3ANABJF3NXQ4VHLHBZI%2F&h=918033dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/EXUBUXT3ANABJF3NXQ4VHLHBZI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n質疑證人拍跌被告致撞沙展 <br />\n官拒納兩差人證供 青年脫襲警罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月3日「旺角再遊行」，示威者途中轉戰黃大仙，並與警方發生衝突。21歲男生被指當天在黃大仙港鐵站出入口襲擊兩名警務人員，被捕後手骨折，更遭控兩項襲警罪，審訊中途其中一罪已被裁定表面證供不成立，案件昨裁決，裁判官指兩名警員證人一人未能準確說出事情，另一人沒說出事實的全部；從辯方呈堂的片段更可見，事情或因其中一名警員證人拍打被告，才導致他跌下撞倒警長，故裁定被告罪名不成立，兼得訟費。<br />\n<br />\n被告嚴世宏（21歲）散庭後透露，過去一年飽受案件困擾，被屈多時終判脫罪。嚴憶述事出突然，他倒地後被人壓住，及後手骨折，事後其手臂肱骨出現螺旋形骨折，雖已過一年，現間中仍會隱隱作痛，無法長時間提重物。他正考慮向警方索償。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LlmREEDqIBfXmh55N3BFs8xjntU=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JPNPZO23K5H4ZCNGKL4ZEUXUPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLlmREEDqIBfXmh55N3BFs8xjntU%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJPNPZO23K5H4ZCNGKL4ZEUXUPA.jpg&h=b461a55e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告嚴世宏脫罪後表示被警員壓至骨折，考慮向警方索償。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方：警方屈示威者慣技<br />\n<br />\n嚴原被控兩項襲警罪，指他於去年8月3日在黃大仙港鐵站D2出口外，襲擊。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n梁官接納警長徐兆雄就被告當時動作的形容，但指徐對於。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n梁官又說，警員麥永祥不否認片中出現於被告近肩膊位置的黑影就是他的手，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據控方指控，警員蔡萬東截查被告身份證，但被告反要求警方出示委任證。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方聆訊時曾質疑，蔡或麥從後推被告仆向徐，製造襲警假象，並。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號： KTCC1503/19<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/umbIICK5G6Dxx7WPCvExaMuk4l0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XDCFHLWFFRDJTPAALSCOGSCY2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FumbIICK5G6Dxx7WPCvExaMuk4l0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXDCFHLWFFRDJTPAALSCOGSCY2A.jpg&h=5a6ac1d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員麥永祥口供不被接納。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a8VEhIgJTh8EciyBUeC_FAYTiLs=/904x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AX2Y5D5SNNEQ5N75AILNVPKAPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa8VEhIgJTh8EciyBUeC_FAYTiLs%3D%2F904x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAX2Y5D5SNNEQ5N75AILNVPKAPQ.jpg&h=577c92e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警長徐兆雄指遭被告撞倒。"},{"pid":"46810aa9c87a3f5e274855f9422248e1d7908811","tid":2174511,"uid":24862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"佢地啲證供 有邊次係可信"},{"pid":"6a530c8ecbe8d231b5696fad5495912c75ee03fd","tid":2174511,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"麥永祥條tie想點....."},{"pid":"21412088e1bd74ce23e2fb5e1571087c148cfed4","tid":2174511,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a530c8ecbe8d231b5696fad5495912c75ee03fd","tid":2174511,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"麥永祥條tie想點....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"小學生啲tie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4442e91fcce08e57667fd311d2bad53b0e376c","tid":2174511,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:51:53.000Z","msg":"假證供冇後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fddbf62a15485a4ed1c62a0adb3a0d37d00bdfc","tid":2174511,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}